PrecisAmendments to the QUEEN'S REGULATIONS AND ORDERS FOR THE CANADIAN FORCES concerning ACQUISITION AND DISPOSAL OF RESIDENTIAL ACCOMMODATION increasing the bridge financing benefits available to members of the Canadian Forces by raising the size of a short term loan, upon which a member can claim interest payments for a period not to exceed twelve months, from 75 to 100 pour cent of the equity in the unsold principal residence.
